ialog","兰迪","你会恨总部吗？","/image/face/002.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","<name>[0]","说不上，战争总是会死人的，我只是恨出卖我们的人。","/image/face/001.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","兰迪","如果总部征召你入伍，你会怎么做？","/image/face/002.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","<name>[0]","我当然会加入，这是为地球的自由而战。","/image/face/001.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","兰迪","我也是，为自由而战。","/image/face/002.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","克雷斯丁娜","真不知道你们在想什么？难道男人都喜欢战场？","/image/face/003.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","兰迪","你说对了，真聪明。","/image/face/002.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","<name>[0]","那么你呢？克雷斯丁娜，你会怎么做？","/image/face/001.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","克雷斯丁娜","虽然不喜欢，但我仍然会加入。你们在那里，我就在那里，不是说好了大家是伙伴吗？我还以为我们不会分开了。","/image/face/003.png",0)Interpreter:doCommand("showMessageDialog","兰迪","对，我们不会分开！","/image/face/002.png",0)